Add the perfect piece for relaxation or a quick nap to your home
with this Darvis leather recliner club chair from Christopher
Knight Home. The dual-function lever reclines the chair and lifts
the foot rest, making it easy to take a quick nap or just lie back.
The neutral appeal of the camel tan polyurethane leather upholstery
helps this club chair blend in with a wide variety of decor styles.
